FBIS4-37244 "drnes118_j_94015" FBIS-NES-94-118 Daily Report 17 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Government To `Retaliate' If `Separatists' Recognized Government To `Retaliate' If `Separatists' Recognized JN1706122094 Baghdad INA in English 1150 GMT 17 Jun 94 JN1706122094 Baghdad INA English BFN [Text] Sanaa, June 17, INA -- Yemeni Planning Minister 'Abd-al-Karim al-Iryani warned against recognizing the separatists in the southern provinces. In press statements published by Yemeni press here today, Mr. al-Iryani said his government would retaliate against such recognition including the severing of diplomatic relations with any country recognizing the separatists.
